api_list.description: Find out the last hackathon I went to.
api_list.code:
import requests

url = "https://maxjmay-maxjmapi-v1.p.rapidapi.com/api/hackathon/last"

headers = {
            "X-RapidAPI-Key": "SIGN-UP-FOR-KEY",
            "X-RapidAPI-Host": "maxjmay-maxjmapi-v1.p.rapidapi.com"
        }

response = requests.get(url, headers=headers)
print(response.json())
